InitBlock.name: LAST_SYND_XPT_DATES

DBMapItem.name: Oracle81
DBMapItem.Value: select max(D.DAY_DT), TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(max(D.DAY_DT), 'yyyy'),'9999') , TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(max(D.DAY_DT), 'MM'), '99'), trunc((TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(max(D.DAY_DT), 'MM'), '99') - 1) / 4 + 1), trunc((TO_NUMBER(TO_CHAR(max(D.DAY_DT), 'MM'), '99') - 1) / 3 + 1), max(D.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) from VALUEOF(OLAPTBO).W_DAY_D D, VALUEOF(OLAPTBO).W_SYND_XPT_T_F S where S.PERIOD_DAY_WID = D.ROW_WID
